snippet.title: Multiplying with a Parabola!
snippet.description:
How can you use a parabola to multiply two numbers? Find out how.

Try this yourself by printing out the graph:
http://www.math.grin.edu/~chamberl/youtube/parabola1.jpg

Online demo at https://www.desmos.com/calculator/mzy5yoaxcz

https://twitter.com/TPointMath

Reloaded to fix a mistaek.
